annotation.value: TypingDNA Reset Profile sequence (not typically used)

1. To set up, go to your TypingDNA dashboard > Verify 2FA tab > Integrations > OIDC Integrations > your Ping integration > Reset Profile Endpoint section > Authentication Secret (copy and paste this secret in the above "TypingDNA check user" settings, as the Authorization param Value)

3. To set up, right-click the TypingDNA Verify connector and chose "Edit Connector", then copy your Client ID and Client Secret from your TypingDNA dashboard > Verify 2FA tab > Integrations > OIDC Integrations > your Ping integration.

2. To set up, go to your TypingDNA dashboard > Verify 2FA tab > Integrations > OIDC Integrations > your Ping integration > Reset Profile Endpoint section > Authentication Secret (copy and paste this secret in the above "TypingDNA reset" settings, as the Authorization param Value)
4. Same as 3 - Verify connector. If you configured 3 correctly this step is NOT required. The same connector is used and only needs to be configured once.
